@MineCraftSlayer, you'll need to look up the original soundtrack discography or check out something like Nipponsei. 
People only ever know OPs and EDs, so this question might go unanswered for a while. Harder to find insert songs, but you can. 
For example "Meteor"(ep 47) and "Akatsuki no Kuruma"(ep 40) were both insert songs in Gundam Seed, but if you'd asked about them then, someone would have points out the op/ed. Lol.

